# .cursor/rules/100-environment-check.mdc
version: 1.0.0
name: Environment Check
description: Automated environment verification for security tools and dependencies
globs: ["*"]
triggers: ["on_project_open"]

<workflow>
Environment check workflow ensures all required tools and configurations are present:

1. Required Tools
- Semgrep
- SonarQube Scanner
- Git
- Docker

2. Language Support
- Java
- Python
- JavaScript/TypeScript
- PHP
- Go
- Rust

3. Security Tools
- OWASP Dependency Check
- Snyk (if available)
- Trivy

4. Verification Steps
- Check tool versions
- Verify configurations
- Validate permissions
- Test tool connectivity
</workflow>